      "date": "2011-10-10 08:11:03.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 6: Verified\n\nconf-sanity test 23a failed with issue LU-726, which is unrelated to this patch set.\n\nI manually verified the patched lustre_start utility on b1_8 branch. It worked correctly with the following test scenarios:\n\n1. Combo MGS/MDT\n\n   1) start servers and clients after reformat\n\n   2) start servers and clients after non-reformat\n\n   3) start servers and clients after writeconf\n\n2. Separate MGS and MDT\n\n   1) start servers and clients after reformat\n\n   2) start servers and clients after non-reformat\n\n   3) start servers and clients after writeconf",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
